CatDescriptText: The banner overhead in the background reads, "Wesley Center AME Zion Out of Debt in 45, Bishop Charles Foggie, Minister J.R. Respass, P. E. Theme Song We Are Marching To Zion".
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of men and women, including Bishop Charles Foggie, Charles "Teenie" Harris with trophy in center, James Dougan with trophy on right, and Atty. Everett Utterback Sr. on second step, in front of Wesley Center AME Zion Church
